      "content": "a TIA? that sounds kinda scary lol. i dont really want to go to the hospital if it's just stress or something. if i take some ibuprofen and just sleep it off, is that usually enough to clear that kind of thing up? i really need to finish this essay by tomorrow so i cant really go to the clinic right now",
